	(text_box "Battery sense circuit\n\nV_BAT is at 4.2 V when fully charged.\nThis circuit draws at most\n4.2 V / 2 MΩ = 2.1 µA.\n\nV_BAT_SENSE is 2.1 V when fully charged and 1.75 V when almost empty."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 209.55 13.97 0)
